search_results.title: Marina Shafir
search_results.snippet: Marina Shafir (Romanian: Marina Șafir; born 14 April 1988) is a Moldovan professional wrestler and former mixed martial artist.

search_results.title: Marina Shafir
search_results.snippet: Her name may be Marina Shafir, but when it comes to combat sports, this decorated judoka is aptly called “The Supernova from Moldova.”
